Package gobblin.converter.serde

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HiveSerDeConverter
    An InstrumentedConverter that takes a Writable record, uses a Hive SerDe to deserialize it, and uses another Hive SerDe to serialize it into a Writable record.
